longBusinessSummary: SolTech Energy Sweden AB (publ) develops, sells, and installs energy and solar cell solutions in Sweden and China. It offers its products for electrical engineering, facade, roofing/sheet metal, electric car charging, and the solar energy industries. SolTech Energy Sweden AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
